Access modifiers										Defualt         private       protected       public  
Accessible inside class									yes				yes				yes				yes
Accessible within the subclass inside the same package	yes				no				yes				yes
Accessible outside the package							no				no				no				yes
Accessible within the subclass outside the package		no				no				yes				yes	
encapsulation:-> hiding the details in implimentation level(private,protected,public)
abstraction:-> hiding the details in design level(read method)        